'''Hadramaut''', '''Hadhramaut''', '''Hadramout''', '''Hadramawt''' or '''Ḥaḍramūt''' ({{lang-ar|حضرموت}} ''Ḥaḍramawt''; [[Ancient South Arabian script|Musnad]]: 𐩢𐩳𐩧𐩣𐩩) is a region on the [[South Arabia|southern end]] of the [[Arabian Peninsula]]. The name is officially retained in [[Hadhramaut Governorate]] of the [[Yemen|Republic of Yemen]]. The people of Hadhramaut are called ''[[Hadhrami people|Hadhrami]]'' and speak [[Hadhrami Arabic]].

Hadramaut, Hadhramaut, Hadramout, Hadramawt ama Ḥaḍḍūt (Carabi: حضرموت ناش: a Mus: 𐩢𐩳𐩧𐩣𐩩) waa gobol ku yaal koonfurta dhammaadkii jasiiradda Carabta. Magaca ayaa si rasmi ah loo sii hayay Guddoomiye ku xigeenka Hadhramaut ee Jamhuuriyadda Yaman. Dadka Hadhramaut waxaa loogu yeeraa Hadhrami iyo Hadhrami Carabi.
